Package de.haukesomm.healthdemo.data

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Measurement
    Created on 23.08.18 This is a data class representing a single fitness measurement consisting of different attributes such as a timestamp, location and vital functions.
    Session
    Created on 24.08.18 This is a data class representing a fitness session consisting of SessionDescription's attributes and a list of measurements.
    SessionAssetReader
    Created on 26.08.18 This class parses the mockup session assets (JSON) in '/assets/sessions/ and converts them into Session objects.
    SessionDatabase
    Created on 23.08.18 This class manages the SQlite database containing all recorded fitness Sessions.
    SessionDescription
    Created on 25.08.18 This is a data class providing basic information about a Session such as it's ID and SessionType.
    SessionDescriptionAdapter
    Created on 29.08.18 This class is a subclass of BaseAdapter and functions as a List- or Spinner-Adapter for session data in form of SessionDescriptions.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    SessionType
    Created on 25.08.18 This enum consists of all available activity/session types.
